title: NFL ATL: Making the Leap; Win Wess’ Toaster returns!
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Making the Leap; Win Wess’ Toaster returns!
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- begins its “Making the Leap” series ahead of the 2014 season, starting with Tampa Bay Buccaneers quarterback Josh McCown. Elsewhere, the gang plays a round of “Win Wess’ Toaster” that must be heard to be believed.
